Concluding provisions
AJNS New Media GmbH has the right to amend this Privacy Policy at any time to ensure its compliance with current legal requirements, or to implement changes to the services in the Privacy Policy, for example, when new services are introduced or changes are made to the website. The new Privacy Policy will then apply when you return to this website.
